{"tid":2454662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨晚鯉魚門黑幫曬馬 一被捕南亞男送院後初步陽性 觀塘警署大消毒","createTime":"2021-03-20T11:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T15:58:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7f59d6960c36b7500906739dbe7235e5203164","tid":2454662,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"昨（19日）晚8時許，鯉魚門三家村牌坊一帶大批黑漢集結，疑吹雞曬馬醞釀廝殺，警方接報派遣大批軍裝警，到場鎮壓並拘捕10多人。其中一名被捕男子，在場表示不適送院，有消息指該男抵達醫院接受檢測後，對武漢肺炎呈初步陽性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/FXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1h8JtbC7zqWsn61__LZDSBVyVI8z3NneUly_I-2XVsBRNl-i2--EQWYU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2FFXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1h8JtbC7zqWsn61__LZDSBVyVI8z3NneUly_I-2XVsBRNl-i2--EQWYU8&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDEyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=0f2837f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2FFXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1h8JtbC7zqWsn61__LZDSBVyVI8z3NneUly_I-2XVsBRNl-i2--EQWYU8&h=489f77a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/FXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1h8JtbC7zqWsn61__LZDSBVyVI8z3NneUly_I-2XVsBRNl-i2--EQWYU8</a>"},{"pid":"15fbb8fef234d7a879d57603f7315906d0e235c3","tid":2454662,"uid":69650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"生化武器"},{"pid":"ef4fac84091515b37f5099fc4c63d